reviews.title: Good start
reviews.comment: Needs to differentiate between pending transactions and posted transactions. Also could use an option for transactions since last log in like the website has. Next update maybe?
reviews.author: Timo H

reviews.title: Not for business accounts
reviews.comment: For personal accounts, I\'d give this app a 4 or 5 star rating, but it won\'t with with my business login info.  Hope they modify this app to work with that soon.
reviews.author: Tanya Kitka

reviews.title: For what it does, it\'s fine.
reviews.comment: Is there a way to include my escrow account and make transfers?  My major quibble is you cannot minimize it without having to wait for it to \'identify\' you, then you must re-enter your password everytime. I hope this app is upgradable. There are many things that I prefer to do online, but not if I have to keep logging in for each transaction or something.   That said, it\'s a great start and I like it. It can do enough to keep me from disaster.
reviews.author: Jack D. Ripper
